 	targetNamespace= "http://www.semanticbits.com/piq-workflow/wsdl/prenormalize">

 <documentation>
	 This document describes a mock service corresponding to the 'prenormalize'
	 node from the PIQ Workflow in Fig 4a of "Parameterized specification,
	 configuration and execution of data-intensive scientific workflows" by
	 Kumar et al.  The prenormalize node takes as input a ProjectedChunkFile and returns an OffsetTileFile and an AverageTileFile.
</documentation>



